              </b>
              will contain between 1 and 6 characters, inclusive.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              Each element of
              <b>
               actions
              </b>
              will contain only digits ('0'-'9') and the characters 'N', 'E', 'S', 'W' and 'D'.
             </td>
